<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idac4b642b-47c4-11f1-8df3-c75a02f6a58e" identifier="/us/usc/t1/s2"><num value="2">§ 2.</num><heading> “County” as including “parish”, and so forth</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The word “county” includes a parish, or any other equivalent subdivision of a State or Territory of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idac4b642c-47c4-11f1-8df3-c75a02f6a58e">(<ref href="/us/act/1947-07-30/ch388">July 30, 1947, ch. 388</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/61/633">61 Stat. 633</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
